onentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),  colors (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":")  and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}}}